            </button>
          </form>

          <p class="mt-3 text-[11px] text-almanac-muted" data-en={`Free daily email. ${daysLive} consecutive pipeline runs. First micro-prediction resolves in ${nearestMicro?.daysUntil ?? '~30'} days.`} data-zh={`免费。已连续跑了 ${daysLive} 天。首个预测 ${nearestMicro?.daysUntil ?? '~30'} 天后揭晓。`}>Free daily email. {daysLive} consecutive pipeline runs. First micro-prediction resolves in {nearestMicro?.daysUntil ?? '~30'} days.</p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-xs text-almanac-muted">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-almanac-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <span data-en="Free forever" data-zh="永远免费">Free forever</span>
